*Istine* su mnogo dragocenije od lazi. (Truths are much more valuable than lies.)

Ne činimo *istinu* da bi bili voljeni. (We don't do the truth to be loved.)

Nije uvek lako reći *istinu*, ali je to uvek ispravno. (It's not always easy to tell the truth, but it's always right.)

*Istinu* se treba izneti na vreme. (The truth should be revealed on time.)

On često govori *istine*, ali retko ih čuje. (He often speaks truths, but rarely hears them.)